## login help
Log in to a provider. OAuth is supported for Anthropic, OpenAI/ChatGPT, and Kimi Code

Usage: imp login [PROVIDER]

Arguments:
  [PROVIDER]  Provider to configure (`anthropic`, `openai`, `kimi`, or `kimi-code`). Defaults to anthropic

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
